            "why_use_en": "<ul>\n<li>Simpler than the <calculator id=\"3318\">CDAI</calculator>, which requires symptoms over the past 7 days.</li>\n<li>Shown to have 93% correlation with the CDAI in the original study (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/6102236\" target=\"_blank\">Harvey 1980</a>), a figure&nbsp;that has been duplicated in subsequent studies (<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/3949241\" target=\"_blank\">Gomes 1986</a>).</li>\n</ul>"
          },
