        "dosing": false,
        "equation_logic_text": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar wellbeing = parseFloat(wellbeing);\nvar abpain = parseFloat(abpain);\nvar stools = parseFloat(stools);\nvar mass = parseFloat(mass);\nvar comp1 = parseFloat(comp1);\nvar comp2 = parseFloat(comp2);\nvar comp3 = parseFloat(comp3);\nvar comp4 = parseFloat(comp4);\nvar comp5 = parseFloat(comp5);\nvar comp6 = parseFloat(comp6);\nvar comp7 = parseFloat(comp7);\nvar comp8 = parseFloat(comp8);\n\nvar score = wellbeing + abpain + stools + mass + comp1 + comp2 + comp3 + comp4 + comp5 + comp6 + comp7 + comp8;\n\nvar index; \n\n\nif (score <5) {\n    index = 'Remission';\n}    \nelse if (score >= 5 && score <=7) { \n    index = 'Mild disease';\n}\nelse if (score >= 8 && score <=16) { \n    index = 'Moderate disease';\n}\nelse {\n    index = 'Severe disease';\n}\n\n//results \ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: index \n    });\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Score',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'Harvey-Bradshaw Index'\n    });\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Index',\n    value: index, \n    value_text: '',\n    message: ''\n});",
